@startuml Application_Lifecycle_States
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
    BorderColor #01579B
}

[*] --> NotStarted : App Install

NotStarted --> SplashScreen : User Launches App
SplashScreen --> LoginScreen : Check Login Status
SplashScreen --> MainScreen : User Already Logged In

LoginScreen --> MainScreen : Login Success
LoginScreen --> MainScreen : Guest Mode

MainScreen --> FeatureScreen : User Selects Function
FeatureScreen --> MainScreen : User Returns

MainScreen --> Background : App Minimized
Background --> MainScreen : App Resumed

MainScreen --> Destroyed : App Closed
FeatureScreen --> Destroyed : App Closed
Destroyed --> [*]


@enduml
